Section1.Para:
The NMMB/BSC-CTM model is a powerful tool for air quality tropospheric studies from global to sub-synoptic scales. The NMMB/BSC-CTM is expected to start providing pre-operational dust forecasts both at global and regional scale within the Sand and Dust Storm-Warning Assessment System (
                  http://sds-was.aemet.es/

                ).
